summary: An underground retreat, accessed by a trapdoor in Breezehome after being lockpicked.
descriptionHtml:
An underground retreat, accessed by a trapdoor in Breezehome after being lockpicked. As of V0.1, it is almost useless, however there is a note with some story present under the desk.
-Note- Please remember that this mod is in very the very early stages of development and is mostly here for my benefit, however ideas are welcome as well as feedback.
author: Icec0ld4
